{"type":"HOSTEL","name":"Waiheke Backpackers Hostel","nameEN":"Waiheke Backpackers Hostel","isActive":true,"isNew":false,"description":"Welcome to Waiheke Backpackers Hostel, your tranquil haven nestled at 421 Sea View Road, Onetangi, Waiheke Island. Our hostel caters to young travelers seeking a peaceful and rejuvenating experience amidst breathtaking natural beauty.\r\n\r\nLocated in a prime spot, our hostel boasts stunning ocean views that will leave you in awe. Immerse yourself in the serenity of our surroundings and take advantage of our close proximity to one of the finest beaches in the country. Within walking distance, you'll discover the pristine shores of Onetangi Beach, inviting you to start your day with a refreshing stroll or invigorating run along the coastline.\r\n\r\nAfter working up an appetite, treat yourself to a culinary adventure at one of the charming beachside cafes, restaurants, or local shops just a stone's throw away. For wine enthusiasts, a short stroll will lead you to a selection of world-renowned vineyards, where you can indulge in delightful wine tastings and soak in the vineyard's scenic charm.\r\n\r\nBack at the hostel, you'll find comfort and convenience awaiting you. Our cozy beds ensure a restful night's sleep after a day of exploration. The fully equipped kitchen provides the opportunity to whip up your favorite meals and share culinary experiences with fellow travelers. Additionally, we offer a BBQ deck where you can savor delicious grilled delicacies while soaking in the panoramic ocean views.\r\n\r\nFor those seeking leisurely activities, our expansive lawn overlooking the ocean offers the perfect space to relax, play games, or simply bask in the sun. Whether you're catching up on a good book or engaging in friendly conversations with other guests, this idyllic setting sets the stage for unforgettable moments.\r\n\r\nWaiheke Backpackers Hostel combines an incredible location, exceptional value for money, and a tranquil atmosph